so many personal feelings with you?

282
00:12:42,270 --> 00:12:45,750
We have a lot in common, I guess.

283
00:12:47,240 --> 00:12:48,360
I'm lost too,

284
00:12:49,840 --> 00:12:50,900
and this company is

285
00:12:51,600 --> 00:12:52,660
the result of that.

286
00:12:54,550 --> 00:12:58,080
