such a disturbed side of me.

291
00:13:15,840 --> 00:13:17,370
But this condition of mine,

292
00:13:18,000 --> 00:13:20,790
it gets better when I take my medication.

293
00:13:30,080 --> 00:13:30,720
What,

294
00:13:30,790 --> 00:13:33,790
are we really going with
Shi Qiangfeng's stupid idea?

295
00:13:35,320 --> 00:13:36,720
How is that his idea?

296
00:13:37,440 --> 00:13:38,320
The expert suggested it.

297
00:13:38,320 --> 00:13:40,200
We were going to investigate anyway.

298
00:13:40,200 --> 00:13:41,240
The expert said

299
00:13:41,750 --> 00:13:43,790
the killer might frequently purchase
women's shoes.

300
00:13:43,790 --> 00:13:44,670
So we should check the shoe sections

301
00:13:44,670 --> 00:13:46,840
in all major department stores
and specialty shops.

302
00:13:46,840 --> 00:13:48,370
Is this for the entire city?

303
00:13:49,790 --> 00:13:51,360
You really don't know the drill.

304
00:13:51,360 --> 00:13:52,270
Not even close.

305
00:13:52,270 --> 00:13:54,080
This is just about one-tenth of them.

306
00:13:54,080 --> 00:13:54,910
Fortunately, there aren't many men

307
00:13:54,910 --> 00:13:56,910
who buy women's shoes by themselves.

308
00:13:56,910 --> 00:14:00,690
Did Jia Beibei take out any
high-interest loans before she was killed?

309
00:14:00,690 --> 00:14:01,870
Before Jia Beibei was killed,

310
00:14:01,870 --> 00:14:04,130
it seems her account
did receive a sum of money,

311
00:14:04,130 --> 00:14:06,410
about 20,000 in cash,

312
00:14:06,720 --> 00:14:09,520
but she apparently didn't get a chance
to spend it.

313
00:14:09,870 --> 00:14:11,600
Bring in Diao for questioning.

314
00:14:11,790 --> 00:14:14,050
Do you know why you're being questioned?

315
00:14:15,030 --> 00:14:16,870
Captain Zhao broke his hand.

316
00:14:16,870 --> 00:14:18,030
That's a serious injury.

317
00:14:18,030 --> 00:14:19,560
I wasn't the one who hit him.

318
00:14:19,800 --> 00:14:21,260
But you bought the hammer.

319
00:14:21,630 --> 00:14:23,000
There's a payment record online.

320
00:14:23,000 --> 00:14:24,800
You provided the murder weapon.

321
00:14:25,150 --> 00:14:26,510
Even though during the arrest,

322
00:14:26,510 --> 00:14:28,310
you were the first to surrender,

323
00:14:28,720 --> 00:14:31,480
aside from the one who actually did it,

324
00:14:31,790 --> 00:14:32,910
you might still end up
getting three, five,

325
00:14:32,910 --> 00:14:34,200
or maybe even ten years

326
00:14:34,550 --> 00:14:36,950
more than the others in jail.
Is it worth it?

327
00:14:38,670 --> 00:14:40,130
Show him the photos again.

328
00:14:45,550 --> 00:14:46,390
You still have a chance to redeem yourself

329
00:14:46,390 --> 00:14:47,990
by making up for your crimes.

330
00:14:53,360 --> 00:14:54,160
I've seen her.

331
00:14:55,560 --> 00:14:57,820
Every cash transaction over 10,000 yuan

332
00:14:58,060 --> 00:14:59,860
had to go through Shark himse...

333
00:15:01,210 --> 00:15:03,570
I mean, Sha Hongli, himself.

334
00:15:05,390 --> 00:15:06,750
He was the one who took her away.

335
00:15:06,750 --> 00:15:10,030
I don't know what happened after that.

336
00:15:11,960 --> 00:15:13,910
Didn't I say he wasn't allowed to go?

337
00:15:13,910 --> 00:15:17,480
He said he'd go to Grandma's house
even if it meant going to jail.

338
00:15:18,600 --> 00:15:20,960
