349
00:15:42,150 --> 00:15:43,670
He wouldn't be that foolish.

350
00:15:43,670 --> 00:15:44,550
I'll go find him.

351
00:15:44,550 --> 00:15:45,360
Don't go.

352
00:15:48,630 --> 00:15:49,240
Hello?

353
00:15:49,270 --> 00:15:50,240
Is this Lian?

354
00:15:50,440 --> 00:15:52,960
I'm Jia from
the Garden Road Traffic Police Station.

355
00:15:52,960 --> 00:15:54,420
When your son was driving,

356
00:15:55,320 --> 00:15:58,000
