365
00:16:10,960 --> 00:16:13,420
Alright then,
I'll get that footage for you.

366
00:16:16,070 --> 00:16:16,800
Who was that?

367
00:16:21,200 --> 00:16:22,000
It's nothing.

368
00:16:24,160 --> 00:16:25,560
Tell his grandfather

369
00:16:25,680 --> 00:16:27,740
