401
00:18:30,440 --> 00:18:31,700
Come on, keep singing.

402
00:18:34,670 --> 00:18:35,060
Sing!

403
00:18:35,310 --> 00:18:36,830
I'll sing. I'll sing.

404
00:18:37,430 --> 00:18:42,600
