00:20:00,590 --> 00:20:01,240
Xiaohai.

427
00:20:03,510 --> 00:20:05,110
Xiaohai, what are you doing?

428
00:20:05,160 --> 00:20:06,490
Come on, let me help you.

429
00:20:09,200 --> 00:20:10,000
This kid.

430
00:20:22,920 --> 00:20:23,780
Don't touch it!

431
00:20:24,750 --> 00:20:26,210
Your hands are all greasy.

432
00:20:39,510 --> 00:20:40,310
Captain Lian.

433
00:20:41,350 --> 00:20:42,400
The victim, Jia Beibei,

434
00:20:42,400 --> 00:20:44,530
used to work at a Japanese restaurant,

435
00:20:44,550 --> 00:20:45,350
Sakura House,

436
00:20:45,920 --> 00:20:48,480
which is on the same street
as Zhang Haoyang's place,

437
00:20:48,480 --> 00:20:49,740
about 500 meters away.

438
00:20:50,670 --> 00:20:51,780
Sakura House?

439
00:20:51,920 --> 00:20:52,440
Yes.

440
00:20:53,000 --> 00:20:54,240
