442
00:20:58,070 --> 00:21:00,000
Go report this to Team Leader Zhao.

443
00:21:01,350 --> 00:21:02,680
But this is our suspect.

444
00:21:02,680 --> 00:21:03,350
Just go.

445
00:21:10,310 --> 00:21:11,310
Team Leader Zhao.

446
00:21:12,030 --> 00:21:14,030
Captain Lian asked me to report this
to you.

447
00:21:14,030 --> 00:21:15,830
They're not far from each other.

448
00:21:16,110 --> 00:21:17,680
He must have eaten there.

449
00:21:18,920 --> 00:21:19,720
Thank you.

450
00:21:20,770 --> 00:21:25,030
Being on the same street doesn't
necessarily mean they ate together, right?

451
00:21:28,110 --> 00:21:30,440
There were napkins from Sakura House

452
00:21:30,550 --> 00:21:32,950
