or something?

484
00:22:54,720 --> 00:22:57,180
Why are you in such a hurry
to make this money?

485
00:22:57,930 --> 00:22:59,190
Shen, what are you doing?

486
00:22:59,190 --> 00:23:00,400
Have you lost your mind?

487
00:23:00,400 --> 00:23:01,790
Yes, I have lost my mind!

488
00:23:02,590 --> 00:23:03,920
It's better to be crazy!

489
00:23:15,640 --> 00:23:16,480
Shen

490
00:23:17,160 --> 00:23:18,640
is just hurting inside.

491
00:23:19,240 --> 00:23:20,790
He'll feel better after letting it out.

492
00:23:20,790 --> 00:23:23,550
Thank you. I'll call it a day.

493
00:23:23,750 --> 00:23:24,680
Please go back.

494
00:23:24,680 --> 00:23:26,810
-Thank you. Thank you.
-It's alright.

495
00:24:19,830 --> 00:24:20,830
When was the last time

496
00:24:20,830 --> 00:24:22,790
