or a simple and elegant one,

551
00:28:07,400 --> 00:28:10,030
but you can't lose your spirit and energy.

552
00:28:10,760 --> 00:28:12,160
Pull yourself together.

553
00:28:12,680 --> 00:28:15,770
He's even lecturing his son
with parallel sentences now.

554
00:28:15,770 --> 00:28:16,450
Wait.

555
00:28:16,830 --> 00:28:18,110
I'll give you the money.

556
00:28:18,110 --> 00:28:19,550
Just do whatever you want.

557
00:28:19,550 --> 00:28:21,280
We're here for investigation.

558
00:28:21,480 --> 00:28:23,400
We don't have to wait for him
to finish lecturing, right?

559
00:28:23,400 --> 00:28:24,660
Let's listen for a bit.

560
00:28:24,920 --> 00:28:26,640
It'll help us

561
00:28:26,640 --> 00:28:29,030
get a sense of how they see Zhang Haoyang.

562
00:28:29,160 --> 00:28:29,920
Keep going.

563
00:28:30,680 --> 00:28:32,830
I'll clear away any trouble

564
00:28:33,240 --> 00:28:35,500
and smooth out any obstacles on your way.

565
00:28:35,880 --> 00:28:37,000
Stand up straight.

566
00:28:37,000 --> 00:28:38,660
Why are all fathers like this,

567
00:28:38,820 --> 00:28:41,310
ignoring what they should take care of
and interfering where they shouldn't?

568
00:28:41,310 --> 00:28:42,400
So dispirited,

569
00:28:42,400 --> 00:28:43,680
like a stray dog!

570
00:28:44,200 --> 00:28:45,860
Can't you show some backbone?

571
00:28:47,400 --> 00:28:49,270
Who are you people?

572
00:28:49,960 --> 00:28:51,290
We're police officers.

573
00:28:54,200 --> 00:28:55,800
There's a case, and we'd like

574
00:28:56,480 --> 00:29:00,410
Zhang Haoyang to come to the station
to assist with the investigation.

575
00:29:03,110 --> 00:29:06,400
Why can't you just ask him questions here?

576
00:29:07,350 --> 00:29:08,550
It's a legal summons.

577
00:29:10,550 --> 00:29:12,930
Let me confirm this with Chief Li.

578
00:29:13,960 --> 00:29:15,960
There's no Chief Li at our precinct.

579
00:29:16,030 --> 00:29:17,110
I'm talking about the city bureau.

580
00:29:17,110 --> 00:29:18,750
No need. I'll go with you.

581
00:29:19,880 --> 00:29:20,880
Stop right there!

582
00:29:23,590 --> 00:29:24,720
Excuse me, Officer.

583
00:29:28,480 --> 00:29:31,830
There's something
I need to inform you about.

584
00:29:32,880 --> 00:29:36,210
Zhang Haoyang has
congenital cerebral vascular stenosis.

585
00:29:36,350 --> 00:29:38,590
Please be careful with your wording
when questioning him

586
00:29:38,590 --> 00:29:39,920
to avoid agitating him.

587
00:29:40,960 --> 00:29:41,880
If possible,

588
00:29:42,800 --> 00:29:44,130
I'd like to have a doctor

589
00:29:44,350 --> 00:29:46,270
on standby during the questioning.

590
00:29:46,270 --> 00:29:47,070
By all means.

591
00:29:47,750 --> 00:29:50,880
We won't be more emotional
with our wording than you are.

592
00:29:57,880 --> 00:29:59,280
We've called you in today

593
00:29:59,510 --> 00:30:00,970
to understand the details

594
00:30:01,240 --> 00:30:03,170
of your meeting with Shen Xiaozhou

595
00:30:03,510 --> 00:30:05,830
on the afternoon of June 19th.

596
00:30:07,880 --> 00:30:10,830
I need you to repeat everything
that was said

597
00:30:11,960 --> 00:30:14,000
and how both of you reacted.

598
00:30:15,200 --> 00:30:16,860
Give me the complete account.

599
00:30:16,960 --> 00:30:18,420
Don't leave anything out.

600
00:30:29,140 --> 00:30:31,300
I'll roll the film,

601
00:30:34,300 --> 00:30:35,700
and you do the voiceover.

602
00:30:55,200 --> 00:30:57,200
What did Shen Xiaozhou say to you?

603
00:30:58,110 --> 00:31:00,030
Look at you, all fired up.

604
00:31:00,160 --> 00:31:01,490
Did she hurt your pride?

605
00:31:01,670 --> 00:31:04,270
Don't tell me it was even harsher
than what your dad said to you.

606
00:31:04,270 --> 00:31:06,270
In that case, surely you'd be angry.

607
00:31:07,830 --> 00:31:09,400
No, I wasn't angry.

608
00:31:11,550 --> 00:31:12,350
It's just that

609
00:31:13,960 --> 00:31:16,400
I asked Xiaozhou if we could talk about it

610
00:31:17,030 --> 00:31:19,880
and start over.

611
00:31:20,030 --> 00:31:22,230
But Xiaozhou thought it would be better

612
00:31:23,830 --> 00:31:25,830
if we didn't see each other anymore.

613
00:31:25,880 --> 00:31:28,790
I felt pretty desperate

614
00:31:28,790 --> 00:31:29,640
and quite agitated.

615
00:31:29,640 --> 00:31:31,570
More like really agitated, right?

616
00:31:32,830 --> 00:31:36,160
Getting so worked up
with your cerebrovascular condition.

617
00:31:37,130 --> 00:31:39,190
Do you have a death wish or something?

618
00:31:41,440 --> 00:31:43,970
Did Shen Xiaozhou know about
your condition?

619
00:31:44,830 --> 00:31:45,550
Yes.

620
00:31:46,590 --> 00:31:49,790
Was that why she didn't want
to be with you?

621
00:31:53,310 --> 00:31:54,310
If it weren't for that,

622
00:31:54,310 --> 00:31:57,310
she probably would've stopped
talking to me long ago.

623
00:31:59,310 --> 00:32:02,070
Was Shen Xiaozhou that important to you?

624
00:32:06,030 --> 00:32:07,480
She was my rock.

625
00:32:12,350 --> 00:32:15,110
You also heard what my father said to me.

626
00:32:15,590 --> 00:32:17,920
He thinks I'm worthless.

627
00:32:18,400 --> 00:32:19,310
He... He's right.

628
00:32:19,310 --> 00:32:20,880
I can't argue with that.

629
00:32:21,510 --> 00:32:24,170
I really don't know
what I want to do with my life.

630
00:32:25,110 --> 00:32:28,440
Only Xiaozhou kept encouraging me

631
00:32:29,880 --> 00:32:31,210
to try different paths.

632
00:32:35,070 --> 00:32:36,530
Now that Xiaozhou is gone,

633
00:32:38,350 --> 00:32:40,750
it doesn't matter which path
I take anymore.

634
00:32:40,750 --> 00:32:43,950
After you parted ways
with Shen Xiaozhou that afternoon,

635
00:32:44,400 --> 00:32:45,800
which route did you take?

636
00:32:46,400 --> 00:32:48,000
What do you mean which route?

637
00:32:48,400 --> 00:32:49,510
The one...

638
00:32:49,510 --> 00:32:51,200
The... The one home, of course.

639
00:32:51,200 --> 00:32:53,110
You took the same route as her.

640
00:32:53,400 --> 00:32:54,790
Were you following her?

641
00:32:55,110 --> 00:32:56,160
H-How could I?

642
00:32:56,160 --> 00:32:57,960
I had no idea where she was going.

643
00:33:02,110 --> 00:33:03,680
Shen Xiaozhou disappeared

644
00:33:03,680 --> 00:33:05,940
right between these two intersections.

645
00:33:08,480 --> 00:33:10,030
Did she get into your car?

646
00:33:11,880 --> 00:33:12,640
No.

647
00:33:20,110 --> 00:33:23,790
Are you suggesting
I could have picked her up?

648
00:33:52,110 --> 00:33:53,660
Either he was telling the truth,

649
00:33:53,660 --> 00:33:55,820
or he's a darn good actor.

650
00:33:56,400 --> 00:33:57,160
Do you buy it?

651
00:33:57,750 --> 00:33:59,680
Don't make subjective judgments.

652
00:33:59,920 --> 00:34:01,350
Keep him in custody for now.

653
00:34:01,350 --> 00:34:02,880
Get a search warrant first.

654
00:34:03,020 --> 00:34:04,420
Search where? His car?

655
00:34:07,350 --> 00:34:09,090
His car, residence,

656
00:34:09,230 --> 00:34:11,190
office, everywhere.

657
00:34:24,550 --> 00:34:25,750
We've got something.

658
00:34:26,070 --> 00:34:27,960
This is from the security camera

659
00:34:27,960 --> 00:34:30,889
at the ATM of China Construction Bank
on Jingwu Road.

660
00:34:31,440 --> 00:34:33,239
Can you confirm it's Sha Hongli?

661
00:34:34,000 --> 00:34:34,880
Well...

662
00:34:36,340 --> 00:34:38,420
It's hard to tell.

663
00:34:39,070 --> 00:34:39,840
But

664
00:34:40,030 --> 00:34:42,429
we found Sha Hongli's car
outside the bank.

665
00:34:44,670 --> 00:34:46,150
Now that he's surfaced, it'll be easier.

666
00:34:46,150 --> 00:34:46,960
Cast the net.

667
00:34:47,510 --> 00:34:48,400
Work overtime

668
00:34:48,739 --> 00:34:50,739
and find him as quickly as possible.

669
00:34:55,360 --> 00:34:56,840
Let's go arrest him. Move.

670
00:34:57,880 --> 00:34:59,590
We... We have a mission.

671
00:35:04,190 --> 00:35:05,560
Okay, just a moment.

672
00:35:06,000 --> 00:35:07,400
Take his bishop and let him move.

673
00:35:07,400 --> 00:35:08,510
Capture his knight.

674
00:35:08,510 --> 00:35:10,910
Just move your advisor
and take his knight.

675
00:35:11,320 --> 00:35:12,190
Don't listen to him.

676
00:35:12,190 --> 00:35:13,710
Moving your bishop is the right move.

677
00:35:13,710 --> 00:35:14,510
Listen to me.

678
00:35:14,840 --> 00:35:15,190
Jump again.

679
00:35:15,190 --> 00:35:17,720
You'll lose if you listen to him,
you know, Li.

680
00:35:20,060 --> 00:35:21,060
You're here, Tao.

681
00:35:21,060 --> 00:35:21,690
Hey, Li.

682
00:35:21,960 --> 00:35:22,880
I've got the liquor ready for you.

683
00:35:22,880 --> 00:35:25,000
Ten cases. Is that enough?
I can get more if needed.

684
00:35:25,000 --> 00:35:25,590
That's enough.

685
00:35:25,590 --> 00:35:27,070
It's just a small gathering,
not many tables.

686
00:35:27,070 --> 00:35:28,510
Alright, have a cigarette.

687
00:35:28,510 --> 00:35:29,230
Thanks.

688
00:35:29,590 --> 00:35:30,230
How's business?

689
00:35:30,230 --> 00:35:30,800
Not bad.

690
00:35:37,920 --> 00:35:39,760
Hurry up, you've been thinking forever.

691
00:35:39,760 --> 00:35:41,090
Don't rush, don't rush.

692
00:35:43,440 --> 00:35:45,240
Tao, what happened to your back?

693
00:35:45,440 --> 00:35:47,440
I was moving stuff the other day
and didn't use proper force.

694
00:35:47,440 --> 00:35:48,440
I twisted it a bit.

695
00:35:49,590 --> 00:35:51,110
A young man like you twisting your back?

696
00:35:51,110 --> 00:35:53,310
How heavy was the stuff you were moving?

697
00:35:56,280 --> 00:35:57,140
By the way, Tao,

698
00:35:57,510 --> 00:35:59,320
I heard your new wife
is a college graduate.

699
00:35:59,320 --> 00:36:00,840
You didn't even finish high school, right?

700
00:36:00,840 --> 00:36:02,500
How did you manage to land her?

701
00:36:02,510 --> 00:36:03,710
Tell me about it.

702
00:36:03,960 --> 00:36:05,160
What's the big deal
about college graduates?

703
00:36:05,160 --> 00:36:06,890
Our factory has plenty of them.

704
00:36:09,030 --> 00:36:09,710
Uncle Shen.

705
00:36:23,630 --> 00:36:24,150
Uncle.

706
00:36:30,400 --> 00:36:32,530
Isn't it a bit early to start drinking?

707
00:36:41,880 --> 00:36:42,670
Tao,

708
00:36:43,030 --> 00:36:44,230
that truck's loaded up.

709
00:36:44,230 --> 00:36:45,670
Why don't you make a delivery run first?

710
00:36:45,670 --> 00:36:46,800
Okay, I'll come back later then.

711
00:36:46,800 --> 00:36:48,330
Alright, drive carefully.

712
00:36:51,230 --> 00:36:53,150
Uncle, I'll leave now.

713
00:37:04,230 --> 00:37:05,960
Shen. Shen.

714
00:37:09,920 --> 00:37:12,280
Stop drinking and go home.

715
00:37:17,710 --> 00:37:18,400
Home?

716
00:37:24,000 --> 00:37:25,150
I've got no home.

717
00:37:38,280 --> 00:37:38,880
Li.

718
00:37:45,450 --> 00:37:46,080
Shen.

719
00:37:46,670 --> 00:37:47,360
Boss,

720
00:37:49,590 --> 00:37:51,030
shave my head clean.

721
00:37:51,670 --> 00:37:53,000
You're drunk.
I don't dare shave your head.

722
00:37:53,000 --> 00:37:55,200
You'll come after me after you sober up.

723
00:37:59,000 --> 00:37:59,510
Shen.

724
00:37:59,510 --> 00:38:00,760
-Shen, that's not for hair cutting.
-Don't move!
